```
# Rust/Cargo specific ignores
target/
Cargo.lock

# Dependencies
vendor/

# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp

# Editor/IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# Cache directories
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.pytest_cache/

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
*.env.*
```